# TB Pro Table Patterns

Reference: `lisa/daily/launch_overview_sample.html` (Tables section, ~340–362).

**Still open queue table:** removed from launch overview design — do not re-add table guidance for it here.

## Base `.tbl`

- Full width, collapsed borders, `.8rem` body text.
- **NEVER `display:flex` (or `inline-flex`) on `th` or `td`.** Flex on table cells breaks column layout — the Ideas table "YIKES" bug came from `th.tbl-sort { display:flex }`.
- **Sort headers:** `th.tbl-sort` — `white-space:nowrap; cursor:pointer; vertical-align:middle; user-select:none`. Label and icon stay on one line via an inner wrapper, not flex on the cell.
- **Sort icon wrapper:** `.tbl-sort__inner { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.2em }` wraps label + icon inside the `<th>`.
- **Sort icon:** child `<span class="tbl-sort__icon" aria-hidden="true">↕</span>` — `font-size:.85em; opacity:.55; line-height:1`.
- **Numeric columns:** `class="num"` on `th`/`td` — `text-align:right; font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums; width:1%; white-space:nowrap`. Right-align via `.tbl .num`, **not** `justify-content` on a flex header.
- **Status dot cells:** `.tbl td:has(> .status-dot){white-space:nowrap}`.

```html
<th class="num tbl-sort" onclick="sortTable('ideasTable',0,'num')">
  <span class="tbl-sort__inner"><span>Votes</span><span class="tbl-sort__icon" aria-hidden="true">↕</span></span>
</th>
```

## Ideas table — Tags column

```css
#ideasTable th:last-child, #ideasTable td:last-child {
  width: 14%; padding-left: var(--space-12);
  font-size: .72rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);
}
```

## Alignment checklist

- Sort header text and ↕ icon on same line — `inline-flex` on `.tbl-sort__inner` inside the `<th>`, never flex on the `<th>` itself.
- Numeric headers right-justified via `.tbl th.num { text-align:right }`, not flex `justify-content`.
- Status label beside dot, never wrapping under it.
